  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 183.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we still live together, and that was a comfort.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I have Frances in St.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Margaret [INAUDIBLE] hospital.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was private, and I had silk pajama.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my husband come with the flowers, because in [FRENCH] hospital, I remember, when Anna was born, he-- it was visiting hours, and nobody comes to me.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You know why?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because it was such a big hospital, he was walking around the hospital with the flower.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't know I have baby already.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyhow, but [? he did in ?] Melbourne.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was in luxury at hospital, and I had beautiful pajamas, and I got flowers.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were not allowed children.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anna was standing on the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Margaret hospital, when I had Frances, it was 42 years ago, or 43, she will be.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The children were not allowed to visit the mother, and I was from the window.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And after, when Frances was still in the pram-- maybe she was six months or eight months-- we started to look for the separate house.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And we found a duplex, because I want to be with my sister, always together.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So so many years we'd been together, they put together money-- my husband and my brother-in-law.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had one kitchen, and we never was any problem.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "[BACKGROUND NOISE] Bless you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And no problem at all-- I was always with my sister, and the duplex was [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we've been, again, together, like door to door.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And Frances was born, and Frances was growing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And that's [? my ?] [? life. ?] And then Anna got three boys, and Frances got three girls.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And I'm a happy grandmother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I just read, not long ago, they said old age is not the wintertime.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "It's a harvest time.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
